==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: lopsided victory
<hw>lop"sid`ed victory</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A victory
in a contest in which one side defeats the other overwhelmingly; -- in
sports, meaning one side scores much more than the other; in war,
meaning one side has many more casualties than the other.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loquacious</ent>⟦br⟧
